{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883384689,"sessionID":"ses_2851a4c3bffeQCXzkVaLGZZ70J","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae5f676001mEE0Hulo1oL6tm","messageID":"msg_d7ae5d128001IDiKIxLYcDVDpZ","sessionID":"ses_2851a4c3bffeQCXzkVaLGZZ70J","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-0b7054a68e414dc08a0b599253b610ad","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-029/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-029/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端 Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端 |\n8: | Module | `sdk-python` |\n9: | Language | Python |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Task Checklist\n16: \n17: ### Phase 1: HTTP Session Configuration (ST-1)\n18: \n19: - [ ] **T1.1**: Implement `DEFAULT_TIMEOUT = 120` constant in `http.py`\n20:   - Purpose: Define default read timeout constant\n21:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n22:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils.http import DEFAULT_TIMEOUT; print(DEFAULT_TIMEOUT)\"`\n23: \n24: - [ ] **T1.2**: Implement `DEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT = 5.0` constant in `http.py`\n25:   - Purpose: Define default connection timeout constant\n26:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n27:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils.http import DEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT; print(DEFAULT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT)\"`\n28: \n29: - [ ] **T1.3**: Implement `DEFAULT_POOL_CONNECTIONS = 10` constant in `http.py`\n30:   - Purpose: Define default connection pool size constant\n31:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n32:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils.http import DEFAULT_POOL_CONNECTIONS; print(DEFAULT_POOL_CONNECTIONS)\"`\n33: \n34: - [ ] **T1.4**: Implement `DEFAULT_POOL_MAXSIZE = 10` constant in `http.py`\n35:   - Purpose: Define default maximum pool connections constant\n36:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n37:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils.http import DEFAULT_POOL_MAXSIZE; print(DEFAULT_POOL_MAXSIZE)\"`\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T1.5**: Enhance `create_session` to accept `timeout` and `connect_timeout` kwargs\n40:   - Purpose: Allow custom timeout configuration on session creation\n41:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n42:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestCreateSessionTimeout -v`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T1.6**: Implement `create_session` with default headers parameter\n45:   - Purpose: Allow setting default headers on session creation\n46:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n47:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestCreateSessionHeaders -v`\n48: \n49: - [ ] **T1.7**: Implement `create_session` with retry configuration parameter\n50:   - Purpose: Allow configuring retry behavior for transient failures\n51:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n52:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestCreateSessionRetry -v`\n53: \n54: ### Phase 2: Retry Handler Implementation (ST-2)\n55: \n56: - [ ] **T2.1**: Implement `RetryConfig` dataclass with `max_retries`, `backoff_factor`, `retry_on` parameters\n57:   - Purpose: Define retry configuration structure\n58:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n59:   - Verification: `pytest sdk-python/tests/test_http_utils.py::TestRetryConfig -v`\n60: \n61: - [ ] **T2.2**: Implement `DEFAULT_RETRY_CONFIG` with `max_retries=3`, `backoff_factor=0.5`\n62:   - Purpose: Define default retry configuration for transient errors\n63:   - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n64:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.utils.http import DEFAULT_RETRY_CONFIG; print(DEFAULT_RETRY_CONFIG)\"`\n65: \n66: - [ ] **T2.3**: Implemen